Problem Statement:
Given an array A[] of size n. The task is to find the largest element in it.


Solution:
public int largest(int arr[], int n)
    {
        int max_Element=0;
        for(int i=0;i<n;++i)
        {
            if(arr[i]>max_Element)
                max_Element=arr[i];
        }
        return max_Element;
    }
